sentences: He enjoyed worldwide success with the single "The Whistle Song" from his 2000 debut album Payback Time.
It peaked at number 5 in the United Kingdom in January 2002, and subsequently, he performed it on BBC Television's Top of the Pops.
The song was a four times platinum selling success in Denmark (200,000 units) in 2000, peaking at number-one on both the singles and dance chart, before its international release in 2002.
